dismissalText.commentary: Aravinda de Silva lbw b Streak 91 (86b 10x4 2x6 137m) SR: 105.81

notes: 1st ever ODI by Zimbabwe in Sri Lanka.

AP Gurusinha and PA de Silva 172 for the 3rd wicket, record ODI partnership for any wicket for Sri Lanka (previous best: 170 for the 2nd wicket v India at Delhi 15th Sep 1982), highest partnership for any wicket in Sri Lanka (previous: 166 for the 2nd wicket, SL v NZ at Colombo (Khettarama Stadium)), 13th highest ever 3rd wicket partnership in ODIs for any country, 3rd highest 3rd wicket partnership in the World Cup.
PA de Silva 91 off 86 balls, 10x4, 2x6, highest ever score for a Sri Lankan in the World Cup, highest ever for any player at the Sinhalese Sports Club Ground.

milestones.description: de Silva has become the top scorer for SL in ODIs with 4933 runs, going past Ranatunga's 4908
de Silva and Gurusinha's 172-run partnership is SL's highest for the 3rd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 150 between de Silva and Hashan Tillakaratne
de Silva and Gurusinha's 172-run partnership is SL's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 170 between Wettimuny and Roy Dias
